	<div class="dr-summary">
		<h3 class="dr-title">Description</h3>
		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p class="">This toddler pancake recipe is based on Austria’s <em>kaiserschmarrn</em>: a fluffy, oven-baked pancake torn into bite-sized pieces. Light, golden, and perfect for dipping into jam or applesauce, it’s a fun and tasty upgrade to the usual breakfast.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->	</div>
	
	
